<h2>Santa’s Elves Hideaway</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13049092/santa.jpg" alt="santaexperience" data-udi="umb://media/81b3a15104164ee3ba1a0f3c9a737429" /></p>
<p>Build the excitement of Christmas and let the glow of festive fun take over, not just from the Northern Lights but from the fire-light of Santa's cosy cabin and the beam of Rudolf's red nose. </p>
<p>Make the spirit of Christmas come alive whilst in Lapland by visiting Santa and his helpers with your family and book your <a data-udi="umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2}" title="Lapland holidays at Christmas">December escape</a>.</p>
<p>What better way than to make the most magical holiday of a life-time even more special! </p>
<h3>Santa's Elves Hideway options available per resort:</h3>
