<h4>See also: <a data-udi="umb://document/a1ca0b20e1a04656bafe955ac5ee88c6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1ca0b20e1a04656bafe955ac5ee88c6}" title="The Santa Experience">The Santa Experience</a> as part of our 7 Night Lapland Adventure holidays.</h4>
<p>*Only available in December, see more on the Santa Experience <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/special-offers/the-santa-experience" target="_blank" title="Santa Experience">here</a>.</p>
