<div></div>
<div></div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13049993/santa.jpg" alt="santainsleigh" data-udi="umb://media/ea02722f7d264695a5cc480ca118eb6e" /><br />
<h3>What’s included in the Santa's Elves Hideaway excursion: </h3>
<p><span>Santa's Elves Hideaway is hidden away in a snowy, candlelit, magic forest - full of atmosphere and</span><span> fun for the children. Visit one of Santa's workshops and make gingerbread with his elves, enjoy the chance to visit Comet the reindeer, take part in Elf school and various snow games for youngsters - tobogganing and snowballs are always on the agenda. Plus of course, there's the highlight of the day - meeting with Santa Claus himself.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13049094/santa-childcare-big.jpg" alt="santaandelves" data-udi="umb://media/7da38d2f0850480285a10e61d1995df6" /></p>
<h3>How to book your Santa's Elves Hideaway excursion:<span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span></h3>
<p><span>You can add excursions to your holiday package via your '<a href="https://my.inghams.co.uk/login">My Booking</a>' portal or you can speak to a member of our UK based team on <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111.</span></span></p>
<p><strong>Please note: </strong>Please do not book both the Santa's Elves Hideaway and Santa Park (part of Santa Breaks Holidays).</p>
<p>*For Saariselka this will be a group meeting with only Inghams guests, this will be around 30 minutes in Santa's home and doesn't include gingerbread. </p>
<p>**In Saariselka guests will visit a reindeer pen rather than a traditional farm.</p>
</div>
</div>
